            . I am groom to 
               <persName id="t18120513-67-person719">
                  Charles 
                  Cleaver
               <interp inst="t18120513-67-person719" type="surname" value="Cleaver"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18120513-67-person719" type="given" value="Charles"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18120513-67-person719" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . The horse-cloth was taken off the horse. The marks were picked out, and the cloth was thrown into the manger. The bridles were found as if throwed out of the window. The saddle was taken off the pegs, and put near the outer door, on a clothes-horse.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I entered the stable about twelve o'clock. The door was a-jar. I never moved any thing.</p>
               <p>
